# Frames Attributes

## frames.delay

The sum of all delayed frame durations in seconds during the lifetime of the span. For more information see [frames delay](https://develop.sentry.dev/sdk/performance/frames-delay/).

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | `integer` |
| Has PII | false |
| Exists in OpenTelemetry | No |
| Example | `5` |
